column5: Picked these guys up before work.  Rig shown as well.
mmm nice looking dinner there and thanks for the rig pic - fish porn and instructions perfect combo

Now that's funny. "Fish porn" LOL. Very sexy looking fish by the way. I too thank you for posting pics of the rig. I don't know why, but I would've never looked at that one. I'm just learning, but I just figured green or brass/copper. Obviously AGAIN I know nothing.  I've heard wallies like purple too?? True??
On sunny days, I like the darker colours.  Our water is gin clear to 35 feet, so the metallics are working very well.
Thanks  for the report, Patches. Nice to see the bait du jour on there as well.
NICE!!!!!!!!!!..  ..gotta love those worm harness walleyes,thanks for sharing...cheers
Great fish. Thanks for the pics.
